# Modulo company

Escopo
- Onboarding e dados da empresa (workspace).
- Perfil da empresa e administracao de servicos.
- Ponto central de dependencia para demais modulos.
- No fluxo atual, onboarding de company acontece somente apos plano ativo.

Rotas e entradas
- Stack: `src/modules/company/presentation/stacks/company.stack.tsx`.
- Base path: `/company`.
- Pages:
  - `landing`: `presentation/pages/landing/landing.page`.
  - `introduction`: `presentation/pages/company-introduction.page` (onboarding).
  - `profile/:id`: `presentation/pages/profile/profile.page`.
  - `services`: `presentation/pages/services/services.page` (admin servicos).
  - `slas`: rota para `@modules/slas/presentation/pages/sla-by-employee`.

Modelos principais
- `CompanyProfileModel` (`interfaces/company.model.ts`): id, name, description, address, imageUrl, wallpaperUrl, phone, rating, reviewsCount, services.
- `CompanyServiceModel` (`interfaces/service.model.ts`): id, title, description, durationMinutes, priceCents, capacity, staffRequired, tags, active, createdAt.
- `CompanyServiceCreatePayload`: payload de criacao.
- `WorkspaceModel` e payloads em `services/companies-api.ts`:
  - accountType, fullName, email, tradeName, employeesCount, industry, primaryService, description, company_profile.

Services
- `company.service.ts`
  - Fonte de verdade do workspace.
  - Persistencia em `localStorage` (key `company.workspace`).
  - `createWorkspace`, `fetchWorkspaceByEmail`, `updateWorkspaceProfile`.
  - `uploadWorkspaceWallpaper` com assinatura e upload direto via XHR.
  - `getCompanyProfile` atualmente mock.
- `companies-api.ts`
  - Endpoints de workspace e profile.
- `company-services.service.ts`
  - CRUD mock local de servicos da empresa.
- `company-workspace.service.ts`
  - CRUD via backend de servicos do workspace (list/create/update).
  - Mapeia campos de API para `CompanyServiceModel`.

Integracoes
- Usado por billing, people, finance, schedule e work-order para obter workspaceId.
- `CompanyProfileModel` usa `ServiceModel` de `clients`.
- `slas` aparece na rota `company/slas`.
- `RedirectIfAuthenticated` so envia para `/company/introduction` quando o usuario ja tem plano ativo.

Guardrails
- Workspace e dependencia central: nao criar services que bypassam `companyService`.
- Qualquer feature que depende de empresa deve validar workspaceId.
- Evitar modificar shape do workspace sem alinhar com backend.
- Nao assumir que todo usuario autenticado ja tem workspace; validar gate de plano antes.
